                <note rend="inline" type="source">816.51/222: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Salvador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hewes</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Salvador</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-12-28T12:00:00-06:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 28, 1922—noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received December 29—12:12 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>120. This Government accepted and signed the terms of the New York Bankers and
                    Mr. Keith yesterday thereby concluding the loan negotiations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hewes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
